@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>About Our Community</h1>
        <p>Learn more about the Gambian Muslim Community in Minnesota</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="about-detailed">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="about-grid">
            <div class="about-content">
                <h2>Our Story</h2>
                <p>The Gambian Muslim Community in Minnesota was established to serve the growing population of Gambian Muslims who have made Minnesota their home. Our community center serves as a beacon of faith, culture, and unity for families seeking to maintain their Islamic identity while embracing their new American life.</p>

                <h2>Our Mission</h2>
                <p>We are dedicated to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Preserving and promoting Islamic teachings and values</li>
                    <li>Maintaining Gambian cultural traditions and heritage</li>
                    <li>Providing spiritual guidance and religious education</li>
                    <li>Supporting community members in their personal and professional growth</li>
                    <li>Building bridges with the broader Minnesota community</li>
                    <li>Assisting new immigrants in their integration process</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Our Leadership</h2>
                <p>Our community is guided by knowledgeable Islamic scholars and dedicated volunteers who work tirelessly to serve our members. Our leadership team consists of:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Imam and Religious Leader</li>
                    <li>Board of Directors</li>
                    <li>Youth Coordinators</li>
                    <li>Women's Committee</li>
                    <li>Education Committee</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Community Programs</h2>
                <p>We offer a wide range of programs designed to serve all age groups and interests within our community:</p>
                
                <div class="programs-list">
                    <div class="program-item">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-child"></i> Youth Programs</h4>
                        <p>Islamic education, sports activities, and leadership development for our young community members.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="program-item">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-female"></i> Women's Programs</h4>
                        <p>Educational workshops, support groups, and cultural events specifically for Muslim women.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="program-item">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-graduation-cap"></i> Adult Education</h4>
                        <p>Arabic language classes, Islamic studies, and professional development workshops.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="program-item">
                        <h4><i class="fas fa-hands-helping"></i> Community Outreach</h4>
                        <p>Charity work, interfaith dialogue, and community service projects.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="about-sidebar">
                <div class="info-box">
                    <h3>Quick Facts</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Established:</strong> 2010</li>
                        <li><strong>Members:</strong> 500+ Families</li>
                        <li><strong>Languages:</strong> English, Arabic, Mandinka, Wolof, Fula</li>
                        <li><strong>Services:</strong> Daily prayers, Education, Community support</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-box">
                    <h3>Visit Us</h3>
                    <p><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> 123 Community Center Drive<br>Minneapolis, MN 55404</p>
                    <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> (612) 555-0123</p>
                    <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> info@gambianmuslimcommunity.org</p>
                    <a asp-action="Contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>